issue.title: Licensed portal for the src helpdesk
issue.body:
This portal should allow the help desk person to search for TA's if the student comes and ask.
 
All the TA's are required to have their photos.

This portal will also contain the remote control to the raspberry pi (or any other device we use).

This portal will only work by license and provided to university as a separate platform.

issue.title: Is there a better alternative of Raspberry Pi?
issue.body: Can we find something that is much efficient and around the same cost as the raspberry pi?
